---
By: Shantidasa
Source:
  ID: 57c5499b-c3b2-4b09-92a9-a6e977a32050
  Locus:
    Page: 476
    Verse: 1
Tags:
  - Truth
---
Truth does not reveal itself in the chatter of conversation, nor can it be
coaxed to betray its secrets upon a printed page. Truth speaks only in the
deep stillness of silence.
